[[File:Bithu.jpg|thumb]]
'''Bithugalgama''' is a village in [[Balangoda]] town of [[Sabaragamuwa Province]], [[Sri Lanka]]. It is 6&nbsp;km away from Balangoda and 24&nbsp;km away from [[Kalthota]]. It is the one of beautiful villages of Balangoda town.

